title: Anggun - Snow On The Sahara
description:
One of her earlier works, where she sounds sexy, mysterious, and intriguing. To me her later works are more techno/disco/eurotrashy.....

Ripped in variable bitrate mp3 on extreme, sounds pretty damn good if ya ask me....
